%section.grid-12
  .width-12.width-lg-8.grid-column-start-lg-2
    #top.linkable-section
      %h1
        Accordions
        %small.label Javascript
      %p
        Pragma encourages the use of accordions for organizing and displaying content for nested information. These can
        be used for FAQs, Comments, etc.
      .notice.notice-icon.notice-info
        .notice-header Information
        .notice-body This component uses designs and functionality of lists and accordions.
    #sample.linkable-section
      %h2 Sample
      %p.h4 List with Accordions
      .list-group.list-elevated.list-outlined
        .list-group-item.accordion
          .accordion-header How can I change my shipping address?
          .accordion-body
            By default, the last used shipping address will be saved into to your Sample Store account. When you are
            checking out your order, the default shipping address will be displayed and you have the option to amend it if
            you need to.
        .list-group-item.accordion
          .accordion-header How do I activate my account?
          .accordion-body
            The instructions to activate your account will be sent to your email once you have submitted the registration
            form. If you did not receive this email, your email service provider’s mailing software may be blocking it.
            You can try checking your junk / spam folder or contact us at help@samplestore.com.
        .list-group-item.accordion
          .accordion-header What do you mean by points? How do I earn it?
          .accordion-body
            Because you are important to us, we want to know what you think about the products. As an added value, every
            time you rate the products you earn points which go straight to your account. 1 point are added to your
            account for every review that you give. You will need those points in order to redeem the sample products. So
            keep rating the products to keep earning points!
